@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontSize 13
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true
skinparam ParticipantPadding 8
skinparam BoxPadding 5
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1.5
hide footbox

actor 操作人员 as User
participant "前端" as FE
participant "SmartSchedulingController" as Ctrl
participant "PlanningSmartServiceImpl" as Svc
participant "SolveServiceImpl" as Solver
database "MySQL" as DB

User -> FE: 提交排产任务信息
FE -> Ctrl: POST /scheduling-task
Ctrl -> Svc: generate(generatePlanningSmartDTO)

group 前置校验
  Svc -> Svc: Redis分布式锁，检查是否正在求解
  Svc -> Svc: 校验策略是否存在且已生效
  Svc -> DB: 加载基础数据（订单、工艺、资源、日历）
  DB --> Svc: 基础数据
end

group 异步排产求解
  Svc -> Solver: solve(planId, strategy, basicData)
  Solver -> Solver: 构建初始可行解，执行MRP计算
  Solver -> Solver: OptaPlanner元启发式搜索求解
  Solver --> Svc: 最优Solution
end

group 保存排产结果
  Svc -> Svc: 校验排程结果合规性
  Svc -> DB: 批量INSERT计划任务
  Svc -> DB: 更新任务状态COMPLETED
end

Svc --> Ctrl: 操作结果
Ctrl --> FE: 成功响应
FE --> User: 提示排产执行中

@enduml